<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta name="description" content="الوكالة الملكية - منصة Kachi للرسايل والمكالمات">
    <title>الوكالة الملكية – Kachi | شغل رسايل ومكالمات من البيت 💎</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Tajawal:wght@400;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0284c7;
            --primary-light: #0ea5e9;
            --primary-lighter: #38bdf8;
            --accent-gold: #f59e0b;
            --accent-gold-dark: #b45309;
            --bg-light: #f0f9ff;
            --text-dark: #0c1e2e;
            --text-light: #64748b;
            --border-color: #93c5fd;
            --success: #10b981;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
        }

        * {
            font-family: 'Tajawal', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            padding-bottom: 90px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .glass-nav {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.2);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .floating-actions {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            right: auto;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 150;
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            width: calc(100% - 40px);
            max-width: 420px;
            min-height: 56px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .btn-pulse-fixed {
            flex: 2;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
            animation: pulseFixed 1.6s infinite;
            padding: 12px 10px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-pulse-fixed:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        @keyframes pulseFixed {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.7); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 15px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(14, 165, 233, 0); }
        }

        .btn-sim-float, .btn-telegram {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px 8px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            white-space: nowrap;
            min-width: 60px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2px;
        }

        .btn-sim-float {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.15);
        }

        .btn-sim-float:hover, .btn-sim-float:active {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .btn-telegram {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0088cc, #26a5e4);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 136, 204, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-telegram:hover, .btn-telegram:active {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #006699, #1a8fc4);
        }

        .btn-sim-float.hidden-float, .btn-telegram.hidden-float {
            display: none;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 16px;
            }
        }

        .gradient-main {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light), var(--primary-lighter));
        }

        .gradient-gold {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-gold-dark), var(--accent-gold));
        }

        .text-gold {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-gold-dark), var(--accent-gold));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px -4px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover, .btn-primary:active {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
        }

        .motivation-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .motivation-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.12);
        }

        .agent-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            font-size: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--accent-gold-dark);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .step-img {
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
        }

        .step-img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .welcome-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 9999;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
        }

        .welcome-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
            border: 2px solid rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.3);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            max-width: 440px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 30px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: slideIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        .welcome-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .welcome-card .features {
            text-align: right;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .welcome-card .features div {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            padding: 10px 14px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.1);
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .btn-enter {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
            color: white;
            padding: 14px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn-enter:hover, .btn-enter:active {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .btn-hero {
            padding: 8px 14px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 2px solid;
            min-width: 100px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-hero-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-light));
            color: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .btn-hero-primary:hover, .btn-hero-primary:active {
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary {
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .btn-hero-secondary:hover, .btn-hero-secondary:active {
            background: #eff6ff;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .price-card, .level-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .price-card:hover, .level-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08);
        }

        .level-card {
            border-right: 6px solid var(--primary-light);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .price-card .icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .price-card .value {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .code-display {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
            padding: 18px 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 2px dashed var(--primary);
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin: 10px 0 16px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            position: relative;
            direction: ltr;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .copy-btn {
            background: rgba(2, 132, 199, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .copy-btn:hover, .copy-btn:active {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
        }

        .code-modal-box, .sim-chat-box, .modal-box {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 28px 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 95%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .code-modal-box {
            max-width: 460px;
        }

        .modal-box {
            max-height: 85vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .step-card, .article-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-right: 6px solid var(--primary-light);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .step-card:hover, .article-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.08);
        }

        .step-card h3, .article-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .video-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 0;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        .video-wrapper iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        .video-wrapper-vertical {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 0;
            padding-bottom: 185%;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .video-wrapper-vertical iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }

        .video-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .sim-message {
            animation: msgSlide 0.4s ease-out;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        @keyframes msgSlide {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(15px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .sim-alert {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 2px solid var(--danger);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 8px 14px;
            margin: 6px 0;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #991b1b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            animation: alertPulse 1.2s infinite alternate;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .sim-alert.success {
            background: #ecfdf5;
            border-color: var(--success);
            color: #065f46;
        }

        .sim-alert.warning {
            background: #fffbeb;
            border-color: var(--warning);
            color: #92400e;
        }

        @keyframes alertPulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.02); }
        }

        .faq-a {
            transition: max-height 0.35s ease, opacity 0.35s ease;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-height: 0;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .faq-a.active {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .faq-q {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 800;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: right;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .faq-q:hover {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .gem-float {
            position: fixed;
            font-size: 2rem;
            animation: gemFly 1.5s ease-out forwards;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 10000;
        }

        @keyframes gemFly {
            0% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0) translateX(0) scale(1);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-100px) translateX(50px) scale(0);
            }
        }

        .sim-reply-btn {
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            background: white;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 800;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideInReply 0.3s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideInReply {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .sim-reply-btn:hover, .sim-reply-btn:active {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .sim-block-btn {
            background: var(--danger);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 900;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            animation: shake 0.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-5px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(5px); }
        }

        .sim-block-btn:hover, .sim-block-btn:active {
            background: #dc2626;
            transform: scale(1.05);
            animation: none;
        }

        .user-msg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #bfdbfe);
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-left: auto;
            max-width: 80%;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .bot-msg {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-right: auto;
            max-width: 80%;
            text-align: right;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 16px;
            }

            .text-2xl {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .text-3xl {
                font-size: 1.875rem;
            }

            .text-4xl {
                font-size: 2.25rem;
            }

            .video-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .hero-buttons {
                gap: 8px;
            }

            .btn-hero {
                font-size: 0.65rem;
                padding: 6px 12px;
                min-width: 90px;
            }

            .floating-actions {
                bottom: 15px;
            }

            .btn-pulse-fixed {
                font-size: 0.7rem;
            }

            .btn-sim-float, .btn-telegram {
                font-size: 0.55rem;
                padding: 8px 4px;
                min-width: 50px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            body {
                padding-bottom: 85px;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 0 12px;
            }

            .welcome-card {
                padding: 24px 20px;
            }

            .welcome-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .code-modal-box, .modal-box {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }

            .step-card, .article-card {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .step-card h3, .article-card h3 {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .code-display {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
                padding: 14px 16px;
            }

            .floating-actions {
                width: calc(100% - 30px);
                gap: 8px;
                bottom: 12px;
                padding: 0 15px;
            }

            .btn-pulse-fixed {
                font-size: 0.65rem;
                padding: 10px 6px;
            }

            .btn-sim-float, .btn-telegram {
                font-size: 0.5rem;
                padding: 6px 3px;
            }
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        button {
            font-family: inherit;
        }

        button, input, textarea {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            appearance: none;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                background: #0f1419;
                color: #e5e7eb;
            }

            .glass-nav {
                background: rgba(15, 20, 25, 0.95);
            }

            .white {
                background: #1a1f26;
                color: #e5e7eb;
            }

            .modal-box, .code-modal-box, .sim-chat-box {
                background: #1a1f26;
                color: #e5e7eb;
            }
        }

        .tips-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-gold);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .tips-section h3 {
            color: var(--accent-gold-dark);
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .tips-section ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .tips-section li {
            color: var(--accent-gold-dark);
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.2);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .tips-section li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- === المحتوى الرئيسي === -->
    <div id="mainContent">
        <!-- === التنقل === -->
        <nav class="glass-nav">
            <div class="nav-container">
                <div style="font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.2rem;">👑 الوكالة الملكية</div>
                <button id="menuBtn" style="background: none; border: none; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;">☰</button>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- === المحتوى === -->
        <div class="container" style="padding: 40px 20px;">
            <!-- === القسم الرئيسي === -->
            <section style="text-align: center; margin: 40px 0;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 20px;" class="text-gold">💎 منصة Kachi – رسايل ومكالمات</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">✨ اشتغلي من موبايلك بسهولة وابدئي تكسبي فوراً</p>
                
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <button class="btn-hero btn-hero-primary" onclick="openCodeModal()">📥 ابدأي الآن</button>
                    <button class="btn-hero btn-hero-secondary" id="detailedExplanationBtn">📖 الشرح المفصل</button>
                </div>

                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900;">✅</p>
                        <p style="font-weight: 800;">رسايل ومكالمات</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center;">
                        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900;">💰</p>
                        <p style="font-weight: 800;">سحب فوري</p>
